        <updateDate>2020-11-04T15:18:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Holding Russia Accountable for Malign Activities Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill directs the President to impose visa- and asset-blocking sanctions on any current or former official of Russia's government involved in the August 20, 2020, poisoning of a Russian opposition leader or the subsequent cover-up of the poisoning. An individual or entity that violates, attempts to violate, conspires to violate, or causes a violation of such sanctions shall be subject to civil and criminal penalties.</p> <p>In addition, the President shall report to Congress on the personal wealth of Russian President Vladimir Putin and his family members.</p> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
